Package mazeFunctions

Class ImageAsset

java.lang.Object
mazeFunctions.ImageAsset
public class ImageAsset extends Object
This class is for keeping track of the images used in the maze as logos etc.

    • ImageAsset

      public ImageAsset(String name, String type, ImageAssetFile file)
      Constructor to set values for the assets details.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the asset instance.
      type - the type of asset this is. Options are logo1, logo2, image1, image2. (names need updating)
      file - the file used for this asset, check that a duplicate isn't being created, reference an existing file if possible.
